data.description: This lovely 1-Story home in Alamo Heights ISD is move-in ready! Featuring a large living room, spacious family room with a cozy fireplace, kitchen with granite counters and stainless steel appliances, a huge pantry/craft room, separate laundry room, primary suite with full bath and well-sized secondary bedrooms. Enjoy the backyard, complete with a covered patio and big lawn space, perfect for entertaining or play, with mature trees and privacy fence. This home is conveniently located nearby shopping, restaurants and SA Airport, with easy access to I-410, US-281, Fort Sam Houston, Olmos Basin Park, SA Zoo and more.  Don't miss this opportunity to make this your next home, book your personal tour today!
